&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9cXDk0qxY0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading">A post shared by Peter Pink-Howitt (@peterhowitt)&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>We Are Dawn&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Shy moon&lt;br>
Hiding with&lt;br>
Dwining stars&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2025/09/shy-moon.webp" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h2>&lt;/h2>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Slow sun&lt;br>
Sauntering o’er&lt;br>
Weald and tor&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2025/09/sun.png" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Green land&lt;br>
Breathing loam&lt;br>
Seeding sky&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://compossible.asym-intel.info/images/uploads/2025/09/loam.webp" alt="">&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Dolphins At Dawn (Off Sandy Bay)</title><link>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2024/06/05/dolphins-at-dawn-off-sandy-bay/</link><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 22:37:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://compossible.asym-intel.info/2024/06/05/dolphins-at-dawn-off-sandy-bay/</guid><description>&lt;p>Palpitating&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Shiver of sea&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Sparkling splinter of&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Numinous ocean&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Gifted personality&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>The Great Green&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Divested of all terror&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Its playfulness distilled to&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Living livery of wave&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>I return new-born&lt;/p>
&lt;p>With Dawn’s&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Rose fingered bloom&lt;/p>
&lt;p>To find you&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Hoping you will&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Humour me&lt;/p>
&lt;p>(It is you who decides&lt;/p>
&lt;p>whether we shall meet&lt;/p>
&lt;p>In the scary deep)&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>Yearning to grasp you&lt;/p>
&lt;p>On this moving&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Merry-go-round&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Of touching&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Not touching&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>Today, will I see:&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>